# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# TESTING WITH FIREBASE EMULATORS (RECOMMENDED)
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# For fully local testing without cloud services:
#   1. Install Firebase CLI: npm install -g firebase-tools
#   2. Initialize emulators: firebase init emulators
#   3. Start emulators: firebase emulators:start
#   4. Use emulator connection variables:
#
# FIRESTORE_EMULATOR_HOST=localhost:8080
# FIREBASE_AUTH_EMULATOR_HOST=localhost:9099
# FIREBASE_STORAGE_EMULATOR_HOST=localhost:9199
#
# See: https://firebase.google.com/docs/emulator-suite
